{"tid":702614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉向中國洩 F-35 隱形戰機機密　勞斯萊斯前工程師被捕","createTime":"2018-06-15T04:56:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T05:14:37.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"29f8c5dde6b0e9e20a1584e4b8c8559185d9ae0a","tid":702614,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:56:13.000Z","msg":"英國汽車及航天引擎製造商勞斯萊斯一名前工程師，懷疑協助中國取得 F35B 隱形戰機的設計機密，涉嫌違反《官方保密法》，在英國當地時間周二（6月12日）被軍情五處拘捕，一旦罪名成立，最高可判囚 14 年。<br />\n<br />\n英國《☭太陽報☭》報道，被捕的前工程師為鍾斯（ Bryn Jones）。據英國《電訊報》報道，軍情五處早前接獲情報，稱美國空軍新一代皇牌 F35B 隱形戰機的相關機密資料，或已落入北京手中，英國當局周二於德比郡拘捕鍾斯，又在他的寓所撿走電腦等物品搜證。但報道稱，鍾斯否認涉案。<br />\n<br />\n73歲的鍾斯曾在勞斯萊斯任職28年，2003年後離職後自設顧問公司，但一直與勞斯萊斯保持聯繫。鍾斯在個人社交網站報稱是中國西安航空學院的客席教授。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n「F-35B」隱形戰機由美國國防公司洛歇馬田製造，屬於第5代戰鬥機，也是歷來造價最貴的戰機，每架造價9200萬英鎊 (約9.6億港元)，戰機具備垂直、短距起降能力。最高時速接近2,000公里，可搭載空對空導彈及激光導向炸彈。英國皇家空軍計劃在2021年前，購入138架「F-35B」隱形戰機。<br />\n<br />\n英國訂購的首批、4架「F-35B」新隱形戰機已於本月飛抵英國，預計年底正式服役。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B6%89%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B4%A9-f-35-%E9%9A%B1%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%B0%E6%A9%9F%E6%A9%9F%E5%AF%86-%E5%8B%9E%E6%96%AF%E8%90%8A%E6%96%AF%E5%89%8D%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B8%AB%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%2590%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B4%25A9-f-35-%25E9%259A%25B1%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25AF%2586-%25E5%258B%259E%25E6%2596%25AF%25E8%2590%258A%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%2F&d=zojaX6QYh3L6vsaSyb2Plv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=90613182\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%2590%2591%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B4%25A9-f-35-%25E9%259A%25B1%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25AF%2586-%25E5%258B%259E%25E6%2596%25AF%25E8%2590%258A%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%2F&h=030a00d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B6%89%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%B4%A9-f-35-%E9%9A%B1%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%B0%E6%A9%9F%E6%A9%9F%E5%AF%86-%E5%8B%9E%E6%96%AF%E8%90%8A%E6%96%AF%E5%89%8D%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B8%AB%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95/</a>"},{"pid":"40679211a543935365a18f8ba3f8d8d40dda7931","tid":702614,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:59:48.000Z","msg":"英國《☭太陽報☭》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩意思？"},{"pid":"bf51077da8b9d7fdcbd4fcd167663a4a18d1b4d8","tid":702614,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40679211a543935365a18f8ba3f8d8d40dda7931","tid":702614,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T04:59:48.000Z","msg":"英國《☭太陽報☭》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩意思？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T05:14:37.000Z","msg":"用咗某位巴打嘅紅底字眼檢查plug in。"}]}